
# Calculator

A simple and responsive Calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Basic arithmetic operations
- Responsive design
- Dark modern UI
- Event Delegation
- Backspace support
- AC (Clear Display)
- Error handling using try...catch
- Prevents multiple operators together
- Result state handling

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)

## Project Structure

CALCULATOR/
